snippet.title: Weaving Tides: 6 Minutes of Gameplay | Gamescom 2020
snippet.description: Check out this exclusive gameplay of Weaving Tides, a charming singleplayer adventure set in a world of magic and textile. Weaving Tides will be released on PC, Mac and Nintendo Switch in late 2020 or early 2021.
